OL,3,CFuneral directors left 46 bodies to
OL,4,Cdecompose in unrefrigerated conditions
OL,6,FVideo captured on bodycam shows in the
OL,7,Finside of Elkin and Bell Funerals.
OL,9,FA Gosport funeral directors that left
OL,10,F46 bodies in an unrefrigerated room,
OL,11,Fsome for more than 30 days, have been
OL,12,Ffound guilty of denying families
OL,13,Flawful burials.
OL,15,FRichard Elkin, 49, and Hayley Bell,
OL,16,F42, were convicted today at Portsmouth
OL,17,FCrown Court following the discovery in
OL,18,FDecember 2023 of serious failings at
OL,19,FElkin and Bell Funerals.
