OL,6,FFollowing a police investigation, it
OL,7,Fwas uncovered that between June 2022
OL,8,Fand December 2023, they kept the
OL,9,Fbodies in the unrefrigerated room,
OL,10,Fletting them decompose.
OL,12,FThey continued providing funeral
OL,13,Fservices despite knowing their
OL,14,Finsolvent business could not meet its
OL,15,Fobligations.
