OL,7,FCrown Court on 19 February 2026.
OL,9,FRachel Robertson, District Crown
OL,10,FProsecutor for CPS Wessex, said:
OL,11,F"Richard Elkin and Hayley Bell were
OL,12,Frightly charged with serious and broad-
OL,13,Franging criminal wrongdoing in
OL,14,Frelation to their funeral business.
