OL,6,F"Today's convictions recognise the
OL,7,Fgravity of their conduct and our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with the families
OL,9,Faffected by the failings of Elkin and
OL,10,FBell."
OL,12,FFollowing the verdict, Assistant Chief
OL,13,FConstable Paul Bartolomeo from
OL,14,FHampshire & Isle of Wight Constabulary
OL,15,Fsaid: "We can all empathise with the
OL,16,Ffamilies connected to this case.
