OL,6,F"We have all lost someone we care
OL,7,Fabout, or will in the future. When
OL,8,Fthat happens, in the worst moment of
OL,9,Four lives, we turn to trusted pillars
OL,10,Fof the community to help, to look
OL,11,Fafter our loved ones, to provide care.
OL,13,F"Mr Elkin and Ms Bell betrayed that
OL,14,Ftrust, and betrayed it in the worst
OL,15,Fway possible.
